high_descs: Turn around then head left, head towards the stove then turn left towards the counter top.
Pick up the potato located in between the square plate and the black pan.
Place the potato in between the knife and the spatula.
Pick up the knife near the potato
Cut the potato with the knife.
Place the knife onto the counter top near the potato.
Pick up a potato slice from the counter.
Turn all the way around then face the sink.
Head towards the sink, then stand in front of it.
Place the potato slice into the microwave located above the sink
Close the door, then turn it on, remove the potato slice from the microwave. Turn all the way around then walk towards the refrigerator.
Place the potato slice on the top shelf next to the apple, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked potato slice inside the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn right and walk past the fridge and turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the potato on the back of the counter.
Look down to face the edge of the counter.
Place the potato on the edge of the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Place the knife on the counter by the potato.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the microwave above the sink.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the fridge.
Place the potato slice on the top shelf in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To heat a potato slice and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Head to the counter that's on the left of the oven
Grab the potato off of the counter
Look down at the counter
Put the potato down on the counter
Grab the knife off of the counter
Cut the potato into slices
Put the knife down on the counter
Grab a slice of potato
Turn around and go to the microwave
Heat the potato in the microwave and then take it out
Turn around and go to the fridge
Put the potato in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Putting a potato slice in the fridge
